# PoPS installed-header contract.
# Paths are relative to include/ and every tracked pops .h/.hpp/.inc is classified exactly once.
#
# api: supported standalone C++ surface; consumers may include these headers directly.
# abi: standalone versioned wire/dynamic-module contracts; changes require ABI regeneration.
# sdk-root: standalone include roots emitted into generated System/AMR/external modules.
# sdk-support: transitive implementation required by installed roots; never a standalone contract.
# test-only: C++ test support; neither installed nor included in the native header signature.
#
# api, abi, sdk-root and sdk-support are all installed and authenticated by POPS_HEADER_SIG.

